{"tid":2363572,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗MeWe，有冇人識前幾年出嘅Vero？","createTime":"2021-01-12T09:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T18:19:44.000Z","uid":246111,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69137fc674ce6607cfd2e5bc580ac6181bb4d23c","tid":2363572,"uid":246111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"近排social media移民潮<br />\nWhatsApp轉去Signal、Facebook轉MeWe<br />\n唔知有冇人識2015年出嘅Vero呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3148/3148722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3148%2F3148722.jpg&h=b40922aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2017年起Instagram更改演算法，改變帖文優先顯示順序兼增加廣告，令不少用家相當反感。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由2018年02月開始，Vero開始喺外國社交媒體圈受關注<br />\n創辦人兼富商哈里里（Ayman Hariri）係黎巴嫩前首相個仔，佢曾指出時下社交平台太多廣告，希望透過Vero讓用家做返真正嘅自己。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Vero除了可以分享照片、影片、文字，跟Instagram不同的是它還可以分享連結、音樂、電影、書、地點資訊，在發文時也能將追蹤者細分為「摯友（close friends）」、「點頭之交」等不同群組，可控程度比起Instagram多元許多。<span class=\"large\">當用家發文時，可以選擇是否讓所有人看到帖文，抑或只讓某級別的人看見。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知Vero又可唔可以帶起Instagram移民潮呢？<br />\n巴絲打請出招"},{"pid":"e0514a7cba2dc6542899264893d3cf33c49a4d94","tid":2363572,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f212c46adb4c033dbf99117b205f7c6403114013","tid":2363572,"uid":387307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"之前D人話用MEWE<br />\n但係FB仲係好多人用<br />\nD人懶得走"},{"pid":"ece3b6f191e76013748eb7639b378bfc26bf41cf","tid":2363572,"uid":267415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42f58ebd767eb0cabb14017d8d8aa7db13febb75","tid":2363572,"uid":264121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f212c46adb4c033dbf99117b205f7c6403114013","tid":2363572,"uid":387307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB